<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2122">‌زِيَادٌ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">‌إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">‌أَيُّوبُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">‌نَافِعٍ </a>نَحْوَ حَدِيثِ ابْنِ عَوْنٍ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«يَلِيهَا ذُو الرَّأْيِ مِنْ آلِ عُمَرَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>